        ],
        "use_name": "commercial uses in large apartment houses near intersections",
        "conditions": [
          "notwithstanding Sections 9(d), 14 and 29(1), an apartment house at or within 120 feet of an intersection containing 100 or more self-contained dwelling units may include commercial uses permitted in Section 38A(1), except a bowling alley, motion picture theatre, service station and billboard",
          "commercial uses must be located on the ground floor and separately accessible from the building exterior"
